# PHP Version Rule

This project uses **PHP 8.3**. The macOS system CLI defaults to PHP 8.5, which is NOT compatible.

## ALWAYS use this PHP binary for ALL project commands:

```
/opt/homebrew/opt/php@8.3/bin/php
```

## Examples:

```bash
# Artisan commands
/opt/homebrew/opt/php@8.3/bin/php artisan migrate
/opt/homebrew/opt/php@8.3/bin/php artisan cache:clear
/opt/homebrew/opt/php@8.3/bin/php artisan make:model Foo

# Composer
/opt/homebrew/opt/php@8.3/bin/php /opt/homebrew/bin/composer install
/opt/homebrew/opt/php@8.3/bin/php /opt/homebrew/bin/composer require some/package

# Tests (Pest)
/opt/homebrew/opt/php@8.3/bin/php vendor/bin/pest

# Pint (code style)
/opt/homebrew/opt/php@8.3/bin/php vendor/bin/pint
```

